item.title: CVE-2023-33967|2024-08-02T15:54:14.183Z -- megaease -- easeprobe
item.description: EaseProbe is a tool that can do health/status checking. An SQL injection issue was discovered in EaseProbe before 2.1.0 when using MySQL/PostgreSQL data checking. This problem has been fixed in v2.1.0.
